Y

YRoller - Class in net.hudup.alg.cf.gfall
Roller algorithm.
Our mining frequent itemsets method is based on the assumption: The larger the support of an item is, the higher its likely that, this item occurs in some itemsets.
YRoller() - Constructor for class net.hudup.alg.cf.gfall.YRoller
Default constructor

YRollerMaxi - Class in net.hudup.alg.cf.gfall
YRoller algorithm may lose some frequent itemsets because there is a case in that some frequent items dont have so high a support (they are not excellent items) and they are in the last of descending ordering.
YRollerMaxi() - Constructor for class net.hudup.alg.cf.gfall.YRollerMaxi
